# Generic SSD16xx-like 2.13 inch starting sequence.
# op data
# 0 = command, 1 = data, 2 = delay cycles, 3 = wait idle, 7 = end
#
# This sequence is intentionally small. Add panel-specific voltage, LUT,
# border, and refresh settings only after verifying the target hardware.
0 12
3 00
0 11
1 03
0 44
1 00
1 0f
0 45
1 00
1 00
1 f9
1 00
0 4e
1 00
0 4f
1 00
1 00
7 00
